2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new framework for zero-shot learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a system that can recognize activities without explicit training. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with activity recognition in videos. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category, but it is mentioned in the paper that the proposed method can be used for recognizing activities in challenging security footage.
